OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779991869
OL,3,CCorrie star joins breast cancer
OL,4,Csurvivors at new cancer college
OL,6,FA new cancer college is set to open
OL,7,Fits doors to patients and trainees
OL,8,Fafter a four-year fundraising campaign.
OL,10,FCoronation Street star Sally Dynevor
OL,11,Fjoined fellow breast cancer survivors
OL,12,Fto look around the The National Breast
OL,13,FImaging Academy, which is aiming to
OL,14,Ftrain 50 new specialists a year.
OL,16,FSally was diagnosed with breast cancer
OL,17,Fin 2009, and is a long-time patron of
OL,18,FPrevent Breast Cancer. She personally
OL,19,Ffundraised for the academy, including
OL,20,Fclimbing Mount Kilimanjaro in
OL,21,FSeptember 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
