FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779991869
OL,3,CCorrie star joins breast cancer
OL,4,Csurvivors at new cancer college
OL,6,FShe said: "Everyone says that early
OL,7,Fdetection is the key to breast cancer
OL,8,Fand it certainly is, it was in my
OL,9,Fcase. I had the mammogram, the tests
OL,10,Fand this is what I want every woman to
OL,11,Fcome and have a mammogram.
OL,13,F"Because it was detected early, i'm
OL,14,Fstill here and i'm so so grateful.
OL,15,FThis is why it's so exciting to have
OL,16,Fit here in the North West."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
