FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779991869
OL,3,CCorrie star joins breast cancer
OL,4,Csurvivors at new cancer college
OL,6,FThe academy houses multiple mammogram
OL,7,Fand ultrasound rooms for trainees to
OL,8,Flearn in, providing appointments for
OL,9,Fas many as 13,000 women a year who
OL,10,Fhave been referred for investigations.
OL,12,FIt also houses the first contrast
OL,13,Fmammogram machine in the North West,
OL,14,Fwhich uses the latest imaging
OL,15,Ftechnology to improve diagnosis in
OL,16,Fyounger women with dense breast tissue.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
