OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779991869
OL,3,CCorrie star joins breast cancer
OL,4,Csurvivors at new cancer college
OL,6,FNikki Barraclough from Prevent Breast
OL,7,FCancer said: "This academy is so
OL,8,Fimportant because it is training the
OL,9,Fnext generation of breast imaging
OL,10,Fexperts.
OL,12,F"Over the years the number of women
OL,13,Fneeding the service has increased but
OL,14,Fcentres across the country have closed
OL,15,Fbecause there's not enough breast
OL,16,Fimaging experts."
OL,18,FShe said imaging is important as it
OL,19,Fallows for quicker diagnosis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779991869
OL,3,CCorrie star joins breast cancer
OL,4,Csurvivors at new cancer college
OL,6,FThe centre stands next to the
OL,7,FNightingale Centre, which is the
OL,8,Fleading breast cancer research centre
OL,9,Fin the country, and was founded by
OL,10,FConsultant Breast Radiologist Dr Mary
OL,11,FWilson in 2007.
OL,13,FShe added: "The machines allow us for
OL,14,Fthe first time in this centre and
OL,15,Facross Greater Manchester to offer
OL,16,Fcontrast mammography which is a way of
OL,17,Fdetecting small breast cancers in
OL,18,Fyounger patients with denser breasts,
OL,19,Fso this will advance our diagnostic
OL,20,Fabilities for the area."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779991869
OL,3,CCorrie star joins breast cancer
OL,4,Csurvivors at new cancer college
OL,6,FRebecca Hartley fell into this
OL,7,Fcategory, having been diagnosed with
OL,8,Fbreast cancer aged 37.
OL,10,FShe said: "It would have been peace of
OL,11,Fmind for me because I would have had a
OL,12,Fnew technology that was made for me.
OL,14,F"I'm here to tell the tale. I was a
OL,15,Fsingle parent. I'm here to be a mum to
OL,16,Fmy now 19-year-old son. Services like
OL,17,Fthat are only going to make this more
OL,18,Fpossible for more women."
OL,20,FSally said her aim is to eradicate
OL,21,Fbreast cancer for the next generation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779991869
OL,3,CCorrie star joins breast cancer
OL,4,Csurvivors at new cancer college
OL,6,F"I've got two daughters and a son so I
OL,7,Fdon't want breast cancer to be a thing
OL,8,Fanymore. I want us to go 'it's just a
OL,9,Fcold' and we can get rid of it
OL,10,Fquickly," she added.
OL,12,F"I've got so many friends that have
OL,13,Fgone through it or are going through
OL,14,Fit and just the thought that we're
OL,15,Fdoing a little something to help is
OL,16,Fjust amazing, and it's in the North
OL,17,FWest."
OL,19,FThe centre is due to open in summer
OL,20,F2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
